    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866880/extras/3a9545e3a39891448cb8329327115504.avif?t=1675183939\" width=600 height=101 /></span><br>1群:362804860(已满）<br>2群:626072182<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866880/extras/3858ee57e95f1ddec3962d6431757b00.avif?t=1675183939\" width=600 height=162 /></span><br>《修仙故事:轮回》是一款像素风动作类roguelike单机游戏, 故事取材于修仙（真）体系。让您在酣畅淋漓的击打体验中，探索轮回的奥义。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866880/extras/3f77442ccfb0d8452529bc2daa0d3ec6.avif?t=1675183939\" width=600 height=162 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各类道具，组合丰富！</h2>游戏物品种类多样，其中包含秘籍、武器、法术、法宝等200多个道具，超过50种组合方式。尝试不同的搭配，发挥出最强大的能力！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866880/extras/b9bcd1051e9052231be54dacf24b5ac4.poster.avif?t=1675183939\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866880/extras/b9bcd1051e9052231be54dacf24b5ac4.webm?t=1675183939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866880/extras/b9bcd1051e9052231be54dacf24b5ac4.mp4?t=1675183939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866880/extras/5a6203148bf086c30cd9b384dedcf00c.poster.avif?t=1675183939\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866880/extras/5a6203148bf086c30cd9b384dedcf00c.webm?t=1675183939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shar